uary 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell me about a deed that will admit me into Paradise.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not be angry and you will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304\u00a02353 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22894,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/05\/09\/abu-darda-dua-akhlaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":34788,"position":1},"title":"Abu Darda on Akhlaq: Supplicating all night for good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Darda reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with them both, stood praying and weeping, saying, \u201cO Allah, you have made my form excellent, so make my character excellent.\u201d He continued until the morning and I said, \u201cO Abu Darda, you did not supplicate for anything but good character!\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33950,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/27\/five-deeds-to-enter-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34788,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Five deeds for the faithful to enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever comes with five deeds, along with faith, will enter Paradise: one who preserves the five prayers, their ablution, their bowings, their prostrations, and their timings, who fasts the month of Ramadan, who performs Hajj pilgrimage\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1420,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/11\/11\/99-names-allah-asma-al-husna\/","url_meta":{"origin":34788,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on 99 Names: Whoever acts upon them enters Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 11, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah has ninety-nine names. Whoever preserves\u00a0them will enter Paradise.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7392, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2677 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32283,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/18\/jannah-remove-obstacles-road\/","url_meta":{"origin":34788,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Roads: Entry into Paradise by removing obstacles","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever pulls something out of the roads of the Muslims that harms them, Allah will record a good deed for him. Whoever has a good deed written for him, Allah will admit him into Paradise by it.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34764,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/23\/spoils-dhikr-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34788,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: The spoils of remembrance is Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the spoils of gathering to remember Allah?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe spoils of the gatherings of remembrance is Paradise.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6651 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Haythami \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\